      "content": "The draft looks fine for a basic announcement, but it's a bit too generic. Our clients expect a very high level of personal touch. Since you've been handling their complex preferences and specific luxury requests for so long, can you add a section explaining how the new system will manage their specific travel profiles? I want to make sure they don't feel like they're losing the personalized service they're used to getting from you.",
